    {
      "text": "A 58-year-old man with chronic obstructive pulmonary disease and hypertension comes to the physician because of shortness of breath 3 days after starting propranolol. His temperature is 36.7°C (98.1°F), pulse is 64/min, respirations are 20/min, and blood pressure is 138/88 mm Hg. Auscultation of the lungs shows diffuse expiratory wheezes. In addition to discontinuing the propranolol, which of the following drugs should be administered?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Salmeterol"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Albuterol"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Prednisone"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Glucagon"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "Tiotropium bromide"
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "text": "Theophylline"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GN0Bcg&anker=Z1f16addecb5bd1d93aae7e4db4f5bcff\" data-learningcard-id=\"GN0Bcg\" data-anker=\"Z1f16addecb5bd1d93aae7e4db4f5bcff\" data-section-id=\"7Ib4VE\" data-sememe-id=\"3RaS54\">Salmeterol</a></span> is a long-acting <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GN0Bcg&anker=Z350eb8cd29b2f98aee1fae10a72648e9\" data-learningcard-id=\"GN0Bcg\" data-anker=\"Z350eb8cd29b2f98aee1fae10a72648e9\" data-sememe-id=\"wn0hvg\">beta-2 agonist</a></span> used as a <span data-sememe-id=\"Vr1GTR0\">maintenance treatment</span> for <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3h0Sdf&anker=Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-learningcard-id=\"3h0Sdf\" data-anker=\"Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-sememe-id=\"Lk0woT\">COPD</a></span> and <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ph0WVf&anker=Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ph0WVf\" data-anker=\"Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-sememe-id=\"Kk0UKT\">asthma</a></span>. Although the <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GN0Bcg&anker=Z350eb8cd29b2f98aee1fae10a72648e9\" data-learningcard-id=\"GN0Bcg\" data-anker=\"Z350eb8cd29b2f98aee1fae10a72648e9\" data-sememe-id=\"wn0hvg\">beta-2 agonist</a></span> effects of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GN0Bcg&anker=Z1f16addecb5bd1d93aae7e4db4f5bcff\" data-learningcard-id=\"GN0Bcg\" data-anker=\"Z1f16addecb5bd1d93aae7e4db4f5bcff\" data-section-id=\"7Ib4VE\" data-sememe-id=\"3RaS54\">salmeterol</a> could potentially reverse <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uN0p1g&anker=Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-learningcard-id=\"uN0p1g\" data-anker=\"Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-section-id=\"RrblSE\" data-sememe-id=\"6RajL4\">propranolol</a>-mediated <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=or00Rh&anker=Z445ba34e92bd5ca4952236c49610dadc\" data-learningcard-id=\"or00Rh\" data-anker=\"Z445ba34e92bd5ca4952236c49610dadc\" data-section-id=\"Vo1Ga30\" data-sememe-id=\"r0Yfhn\">bronchospasm</a> in this patient, the drug is not recommended for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">acute exacerbations of COPD</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GN0Bcg&anker=Z4a4150a87542490cc222fcb6f3f2bd8a\" data-learningcard-id=\"GN0Bcg\" data-anker=\"Z4a4150a87542490cc222fcb6f3f2bd8a\" data-section-id=\"7Ib4VE\" data-sememe-id=\"hRac54\">Albuterol</a> is a short-acting <span class=\"wichtig\"><b><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GN0Bcg&anker=Z350eb8cd29b2f98aee1fae10a72648e9\" data-learningcard-id=\"GN0Bcg\" data-anker=\"Z350eb8cd29b2f98aee1fae10a72648e9\" data-sememe-id=\"wn0hvg\">beta-2 adrenergic agonist</a></b></span> that induces relaxation of bronchial <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=so0tWS&anker=Z866ed9d8301f816f0335f83c58f7c562\" data-learningcard-id=\"so0tWS\" data-anker=\"Z866ed9d8301f816f0335f83c58f7c562\" data-section-id=\"szct8U0\" data-sememe-id=\"cdXaKC\">smooth muscle cells</a>. A patient presenting with signs of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">acute exacerbation of COPD</a> (e.g., <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Xq09CS&anker=Zec7af3634c75f9e5227d266d823e5ea7\" data-learningcard-id=\"Xq09CS\" data-anker=\"Zec7af3634c75f9e5227d266d823e5ea7\" data-sememe-id=\"KaYUln\">shortness of breath</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Z9f745914c0340ad3beed72e989c555ff\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Z9f745914c0340ad3beed72e989c555ff\" data-section-id=\"sCXttZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"Jj0sYT\">tachypnea</a>, and expiratory <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=tl0XAT&anker=Ze1c6d6b140663b2d56aebcff926e0252\" data-learningcard-id=\"tl0XAT\" data-anker=\"Ze1c6d6b140663b2d56aebcff926e0252\" data-section-id=\"8CXOFZ0\" data-sememe-id=\"DQb1yt\">wheezes</a>) shortly after starting <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uN0p1g&anker=Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-learningcard-id=\"uN0p1g\" data-anker=\"Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-section-id=\"RrblSE\" data-sememe-id=\"6RajL4\">propranolol</a>, most likely has drug-induced <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=or00Rh&anker=Z445ba34e92bd5ca4952236c49610dadc\" data-learningcard-id=\"or00Rh\" data-anker=\"Z445ba34e92bd5ca4952236c49610dadc\" data-section-id=\"Vo1Ga30\" data-sememe-id=\"r0Yfhn\">bronchospasm</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GN0Bcg&anker=Z4a4150a87542490cc222fcb6f3f2bd8a\" data-learningcard-id=\"GN0Bcg\" data-anker=\"Z4a4150a87542490cc222fcb6f3f2bd8a\" data-section-id=\"7Ib4VE\" data-sememe-id=\"hRac54\">Albuterol</a> is typically used as a first-line <span class=\"wichtig\"><b><span data-sememe-id=\"k4bmjF\">bronchodilator</span></b></span> in patients with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">acute exacerbation of COPD</a> or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ph0WVf&anker=Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ph0WVf\" data-anker=\"Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-sememe-id=\"Kk0UKT\">asthma</a> and would counteract the effect of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uN0p1g&anker=Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-learningcard-id=\"uN0p1g\" data-anker=\"Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-section-id=\"RrblSE\" data-sememe-id=\"6RajL4\">propranolol</a> seen in this patient.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sememe-id=\"YOanIk\">Prednisone</a></span> is a systemic <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-section-id=\"Pq1WA30\" data-sememe-id=\"8AbOlw\">corticosteroid</a></span> that reduces inflammation by suppressing the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=1K022S&anker=Zec78b6e5eb50f21c8c46330bb0b1ab45\" data-learningcard-id=\"1K022S\" data-anker=\"Zec78b6e5eb50f21c8c46330bb0b1ab45\" data-section-id=\"-JcD9W0\">immune response</a>. Although <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z7acc6b8a4fb3eecc9bdffe7ff1f88c25\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sememe-id=\"YOanIk\">prednisone</a> is frequently used for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">acute exacerbations of COPD</a>, it would not be the first-line treatment in a patient with drug-induced <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=or00Rh&anker=Z445ba34e92bd5ca4952236c49610dadc\" data-learningcard-id=\"or00Rh\" data-anker=\"Z445ba34e92bd5ca4952236c49610dadc\" data-section-id=\"Vo1Ga30\" data-sememe-id=\"r0Yfhn\">bronchospasm</a></span>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=260T4S&anker=Zee82769cbb8a350ab35aba8d36b7f104\" data-learningcard-id=\"260T4S\" data-anker=\"Zee82769cbb8a350ab35aba8d36b7f104\" data-section-id=\"TFc6hV0\" data-sememe-id=\"l9bvnD\">Glucagon</a></span> increases intracellular <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=qo0C1S&anker=Z64a7426bbad2bf440e8e5d9e67c2a51a\" data-learningcard-id=\"qo0C1S\" data-anker=\"Z64a7426bbad2bf440e8e5d9e67c2a51a\" data-section-id=\"QocubW0\" data-sememe-id=\"VGbGyE\">cAMP</a></span> by activating <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=qo0C1S&anker=Z6f7a1ab6b8e1feab20614ec0d1931007\" data-learningcard-id=\"qo0C1S\" data-anker=\"Z6f7a1ab6b8e1feab20614ec0d1931007\" data-section-id=\"QocubW0\" data-sememe-id=\"6VXjvC\">adenylate cyclase</a></span>. Intravenous <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=260T4S&anker=Zee82769cbb8a350ab35aba8d36b7f104\" data-learningcard-id=\"260T4S\" data-anker=\"Zee82769cbb8a350ab35aba8d36b7f104\" data-section-id=\"TFc6hV0\" data-sememe-id=\"l9bvnD\">glucagon</a> can be used for the initial treatment of patients with severe <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zd260d8e17660a21cb9baf0a449c178d7\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zd260d8e17660a21cb9baf0a449c178d7\" data-section-id=\"KVcUvY0\" data-sememe-id=\"Fh0gff\">bradycardia</a></span> and <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Zb5022b8fa3fa419ab039a0f8d70866a2\" data-section-id=\"oVc0vY0\" data-sememe-id=\"nGb7-E\">hypotension</a></span> secondary to <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uN0p1g&anker=Z646f3b357e1aa1b674b6db003136f919\" data-learningcard-id=\"uN0p1g\" data-anker=\"Z646f3b357e1aa1b674b6db003136f919\" data-sememe-id=\"xn0Evg\">beta blocker</a></span> overdose. Although this patient's symptoms are most likely due to side effects of <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=uN0p1g&anker=Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-learningcard-id=\"uN0p1g\" data-anker=\"Z65f2e6f22b24b36f9fcb364dfafeee74\" data-section-id=\"RrblSE\" data-sememe-id=\"6RajL4\">propranolol</a></span>, <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=260T4S&anker=Zee82769cbb8a350ab35aba8d36b7f104\" data-learningcard-id=\"260T4S\" data-anker=\"Zee82769cbb8a350ab35aba8d36b7f104\" data-section-id=\"TFc6hV0\" data-sememe-id=\"l9bvnD\">glucagon</a></span> is not used to treat <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">acute exacerbations of COPD</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=sN0tcg&anker=Z65a36e01f51448c438f74cc289c7520d\" data-learningcard-id=\"sN0tcg\" data-anker=\"Z65a36e01f51448c438f74cc289c7520d\" data-section-id=\"lIbv1E\" data-sememe-id=\"-3aDO4\">Tiotropium bromide</a> is a long-acting <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=sN0tcg&anker=Z8a48999eb24db3f3ead254646577306f\" data-learningcard-id=\"sN0tcg\" data-anker=\"Z8a48999eb24db3f3ead254646577306f\" data-sememe-id=\"FRbgKt\">antimuscarinic agent</a></span> that <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7N04cg&anker=Zc1a5e794a2b47041247eb0df9774c5b9\" data-learningcard-id=\"7N04cg\" data-anker=\"Zc1a5e794a2b47041247eb0df9774c5b9\" data-section-id=\"gBXFZ00\" data-sememe-id=\"w7XhLz\">competitively inhibits</a> the action of <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=lp0vpS&anker=Z3c3ab1c3772cabdb26be3c413ba52df4\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-anker=\"Z3c3ab1c3772cabdb26be3c413ba52df4\" data-section-id=\"VCcGIe0\" data-sememe-id=\"seXtZx\">acetylcholine</a></span> in bronchial <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=so0tWS&anker=Z866ed9d8301f816f0335f83c58f7c562\" data-learningcard-id=\"so0tWS\" data-anker=\"Z866ed9d8301f816f0335f83c58f7c562\" data-section-id=\"szct8U0\" data-sememe-id=\"cdXaKC\">smooth muscle cells</a></span>, causing bronchodilation. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=sN0tcg&anker=Z65a36e01f51448c438f74cc289c7520d\" data-learningcard-id=\"sN0tcg\" data-anker=\"Z65a36e01f51448c438f74cc289c7520d\" data-section-id=\"lIbv1E\" data-sememe-id=\"-3aDO4\">Tiotropium bromide</a> is used as a <span data-sememe-id=\"Vr1GTR0\">maintenance treatment</span> for <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3h0Sdf&anker=Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-learningcard-id=\"3h0Sdf\" data-anker=\"Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-sememe-id=\"Lk0woT\">COPD</a></span> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ph0WVf&anker=Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ph0WVf\" data-anker=\"Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-sememe-id=\"Kk0UKT\">asthma</a>, but it is not used to treat <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">acute exacerbations of COPD</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>F) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=em0xeg&anker=Z7c1394ed7b7c373863e0add18e08a73b\" data-learningcard-id=\"em0xeg\" data-anker=\"Z7c1394ed7b7c373863e0add18e08a73b\" data-section-id=\"jtb_Wv\" data-sememe-id=\"o900oR\">Theophylline</a></span> is a <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=em0xeg&anker=Z6d43f3e86b92fb5db987777e7c031149\" data-learningcard-id=\"em0xeg\" data-anker=\"Z6d43f3e86b92fb5db987777e7c031149\" data-sememe-id=\"TL06Cg\">phosphodiesterase inhibitor</a></span> with anti-inflammatory and bronchodilatory effects used for the treatment of chronic <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3h0Sdf&anker=Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-learningcard-id=\"3h0Sdf\" data-anker=\"Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-sememe-id=\"Lk0woT\">COPD</a></span> and <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ph0WVf&anker=Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ph0WVf\" data-anker=\"Z03da7ad267ef3d61ce133d6c12f67140\" data-sememe-id=\"Kk0UKT\">asthma</a></span>. <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=em0xeg&anker=Zdcde7567fb7e0eda77efcac9cbc00ff3\" data-learningcard-id=\"em0xeg\" data-anker=\"Zdcde7567fb7e0eda77efcac9cbc00ff3\" data-section-id=\"jtb_Wv\" data-sememe-id=\"HvbKYD\">Methylxanthines</a></span> such as <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=em0xeg&anker=Z7c1394ed7b7c373863e0add18e08a73b\" data-learningcard-id=\"em0xeg\" data-anker=\"Z7c1394ed7b7c373863e0add18e08a73b\" data-section-id=\"jtb_Wv\" data-sememe-id=\"o900oR\">theophylline</a> are not recommended for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=TI06Xh&anker=Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-learningcard-id=\"TI06Xh\" data-anker=\"Zeef29a2f76ef553bab54b6f3cdbb5fb6\" data-sememe-id=\"2ibTIt\">acute exacerbations of COPD</a> because they have a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7N04cg&anker=Z5b0cea2cb2a1e89b35ef8f9de1c28356\" data-learningcard-id=\"7N04cg\" data-anker=\"Z5b0cea2cb2a1e89b35ef8f9de1c28356\" data-section-id=\"gBXFZ00\" data-sememe-id=\"WFbPSv\">narrow therapeutic index</a> and can have significant adverse effects, including <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7S04af&anker=Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"7S04af\" data-anker=\"Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-sememe-id=\"Yk0nmT\">cardiac arrhythmias</a></span> and <span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=lp0vpS&anker=Z0111aade770ed6f7d136b455de1d6c1f\" data-learningcard-id=\"lp0vpS\" data-anker=\"Z0111aade770ed6f7d136b455de1d6c1f\" data-section-id=\"1Cc2Ie0\" data-sememe-id=\"6SXj0B\">CNS</a></span> excitation. The risk of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7S04af&anker=Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"7S04af\" data-anker=\"Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-sememe-id=\"Yk0nmT\">cardiac arrhythmias</a> is especially concerning because patients with severe <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=3h0Sdf&anker=Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-learningcard-id=\"3h0Sdf\" data-anker=\"Ze02d225158d496610d00b7f2469fca56\" data-sememe-id=\"Lk0woT\">COPD</a> often have concurrent cardiovascular disease (<span class=\"linksuggest\"><a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=w50hmg&anker=Zbdd462a62be9df381b0ee521bc61881d\" data-learningcard-id=\"w50hmg\" data-anker=\"Zbdd462a62be9df381b0ee521bc61881d\" data-section-id=\"rXWfzP0\" data-sememe-id=\"PmaWfO\">cor pulmonale</a></span>), which increases the baseline risk of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=7S04af&anker=Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-learningcard-id=\"7S04af\" data-anker=\"Ze688ba61de47d1456aee769e72c55a4c\" data-sememe-id=\"Yk0nmT\">arrhythmias</a>.</div>",
      "hint": "Propranolol is a non-selective beta blocker. Beta-2 blockade can trigger bronchoconstriction, particularly in patients with COPD or asthma.",
